POST localhost:8080/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Event Name",
  "description": "Event Description",
  "settings": {
    "numberOfSeats": 100
  }
}

### Get all events
GET localhost:8080/events?page=0&size=10

### Get a specific event by ID
GET localhost:8080/events/2

### Get seats by event ID
GET localhost:8080/events/1/seats
